caption:
Thank you to @connectRNapp for sponsoring this event to bring Baltimore nurses and CNAs together for a chance to connect and unwind.

I’m so grateful to each and every person that came out, shared their story over great food and drinks, and made this a night to remember! 

Make sure you don’t miss another nurses night out or nurses connect event! Follow @connectRNapp so you’re in the know when they’re hosting an event it your city!

Comment your city here. I want to see where y’all are at!
